description: The Twisted Indian truck is taking tastiness through the streets of Tampa Bay, with their incredibly delicious Indian fusion cuisine. Founders Elaine & Lokesh together took their collective culinary experience and passion for making unforgettable food, to form The Twisted Indian. With their ever-so-innovative “Naanwich”- authentic naan filled with your choice of protein, and topped with sauteed peppers & onions, fresh spinach, cilantro, and Raita yoghurt sauce, as well as all their other curry creations, this truck is quickly becoming a local favorite. Southern Living Magazine has listed this truck as one of the best, so you better be making your way to The Twisted Indian soon so that you can try a taste of this acclaimed worldly fare.
name: The Twisted Indian
